name: Space Travel (jisase)
description:
Join this space adventure where your only mission is to survive.

On a space exploration mission, your ship was hit by a gamma ray burst that caused you to drift and your ship started to grow every second, but the explosion also created energy orbs that you can survive with, maybe....

-------------------------------------------------- -------------------------------------------

Space Travel is an 'endless runner' mixed with the mythical spaceship arcade games and taken to 3D completely offline in which your only mission is to hold on alive as long as possible, here time is money and money will allow you to buy different ships, each ship has an ability, like shooting, or a shield and in turn each of the ships has different stats, so you can choose a ship that suits your play style.

Space travel features: 

- More than 20 ships with different stats.

- 4 different skills

- 6 unique items

- 50 missions 

-------------------------------------------------- -------------------------------------------

All content is available without additional payments
